om/trademark_bot/status/721918697921777664 a tweet] of their trademark on April 17, 2016.\n\n===Origin===\nPopplio may be based on a {{wp|sea lion}} with elements of a {{wp|circus clown}}.\n\n====Name origin====\nPopplio may be a combination of \'\'sea lion pup\'\', \'\'pop\'\', \'\'pōpō\'\' (Hawaiian for ball), and \'\'ʻīlio-holo-i-ka-uaua\'\' (Hawaiian for the {{wp|Hawaiian monk seal}}; meaning "dog that runs in rough water").\n\nAshimari may be a combination of 海驢 \'\'ashika\'\' (sea lion), 鞠 \'\'mari\'\' (ball), and \'\'marine\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Water|type2=Water\n|ja=アシマリ \'\'Ashimari\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|海驢 \'\'ashika\'\'|sea lion}}, {{tt|鞠 \'\'mari\'\'|ball}}, and \'\'marine\'\'\n|fr=Otaquin|frmeaning=From \'\'{{tt|otarie|sea lion}}\'\', \'\'{{tt|taquin|playful}}\'\', and \'\'{{tt|arlequin|harlequin}}\'\'\n|es=Popplio|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Robball|demeaning=From {{tt|\'\'Robbe\'\'|seal}} and \'\'Ball\'\'\n|it=Popplio|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=누리공 \'\'Nurigong\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|온눌 \'\'onnul\'\'|fur seal}} and {{tt|공 \'\'gong\'\'|ball}}\n|zh_cmn=球球海獅 / 球球海狮 \'\'Qiúqiúhǎishī\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|球 \'\'qiú\'\'|ball}} and {{tt|海獅 / 海狮 \'\'hǎishī\'\'|sea lion}}\n|zh_yue=球球海獅 \'\'Kàuhkàuhhóisī\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=From {{tt|球 \'\'kàuh\'\'|ball}} and {{tt|海獅 \'\'hóisī\'\'|sea lion}}\n|he=פופליו \'\'Popplio\'\'|hemeaning=Transcription of English name\n|ru=Попплио \'\'Popplio\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name}}\n{{-}}\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Lana\'s Popplio]]\n* [[Starter Pokémon]]\n\n==Notes==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n{{Starter Pokémon|Water}}\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Water}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Water|prevnum=727|prev=Incineroar|nextnum=729|next=Brionne}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[Category:Starter Pokémon|728]]\n\n[[de:Robball]]\n[[es:Popplio]]\n[[fr:Otaquin]]\n[[it:Popplio]]\n[[ja:アシマリ]]\n[[zh:球球海狮]]'}